OL,3,CSchool's artificial intelligence
OL,4,Chelping raise kids' self esteem
OL,6,Fby Rory O'Regan
OL,8,FArtificial Intelligence is allowing
OL,9,Fstudents at special schools to thrive
OL,10,Fand learn in ways that would have
OL,11,Fpreviously been impossible, according
OL,12,Fto their teachers.
OL,14,FClifton School in Bangor is one of
OL,15,Fthree special schools that has taken
OL,16,Fpart in a pilot run the Education
OL,17,FAuthority.
OL,19,FPupils have been able to experiment
OL,20,Fwith the software to develop their own
OL,21,Fpieces of art, as well as create music.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
