OL,3,CSchool's artificial intelligence
OL,4,Chelping raise kids' self esteem
OL,6,F"It brings us closer to the child,"
OL,7,Fsaid John-Michael Greeves, who is the
OL,8,Fschool's art coordinator.
OL,10,F"We're listening rather than just
OL,11,Fsaying 'you're gonna make these
OL,12,Fhandprints today'. Instead, it's 'what
OL,13,Fwould you like to make today'?"
OL,15,FThe technology works by teachers
OL,16,Fasking the students to pick one of two
OL,17,Fprompts on the screen, e.g. big or
OL,18,Fsmall, happy or sad.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
