OL,6,FThey then ask them to list a few of
OL,7,Ftheir favourite things; for example,
OL,8,FDalton, a student at the school,
OL,9,Fpicked Henry the Hoover and prawn
OL,10,Fcocktail flavoured crisps.
OL,12,FUsing the information he supplied, the
OL,13,FAI tool generated a number of images
OL,14,Fbased on his choices.
OL,16,FHis mum, Zoe Fusco, said being
OL,17,Fcreative in this way has boosted his
OL,18,Fself-esteem.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
