OL,3,CSchool's artificial intelligence
OL,4,Chelping raise kids' self esteem
OL,6,F"He's really, really confident in what
OL,7,Fhe's doing and he's so proud to show
OL,8,Fhis work to everyone," she said.
OL,10,F"He brings it everywhere, the wee
OL,11,Fprint out of it, he loves it. He's
OL,12,Fconstantly wanting to redo it. He's so
OL,13,Fexcited to come into school and to be
OL,14,Fable to do this.
OL,16,F"He couldn't make that type of art
OL,17,Findependently without that equipment,
OL,18,Fwhich is amazing."
OL,20,FThe software can also be used to make
OL,21,Fmusic.
