OL,3,CSchool's artificial intelligence
OL,4,Chelping raise kids' self esteem
OL,6,FClifton's students have produced a
OL,7,Fsong called 'Rise' which was generated
OL,8,Fusing AI using lyrics they chose.
OL,10,FMany of the pupils are non-verbal, so
OL,11,Ftheir teachers say creating music
OL,12,Fgives them a voice.
OL,14,FBrenda Mullan, who is the school's
OL,15,Fvice principal said: "They see the
OL,16,Fproduct of their work as theirs, not
OL,17,Fsomething that they have been
OL,18,Fsupported with to a really high level
OL,19,Fby a member of staff.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
