OL,3,CSchool's artificial intelligence
OL,4,Chelping raise kids' self esteem
OL,6,F"They're seeing their ideas, their
OL,7,Ffeelings, their interests and their
OL,8,Fstrengths interwoven into their pieces
OL,9,Fof artwork, but also their songs that
OL,10,Fthey've produced.
OL,12,F"And what a great way to raise self-
OL,13,Festeem and that sense of achievement
OL,14,Ffor our children and young people, to
OL,15,Fcelebrate that with them.
OL,17,F"It has been a game changer for us."
